{"id": 59695, "date": "2025-09-22T04:00:23", "date_gmt": "2025-09-22T11:00:23", "guid": {"rendered": "https://estreetshuffle.com/?p=59695"}, "modified": "2026-05-25T09:06:31", "modified_gmt": "2026-05-25T16:06:31", "slug": "kingdom-of-days-september-22-2", "status": "publish", "type": "post", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/09/22/kingdom-of-days-september-22-2/", "title": {"rendered": "September 22"}, "content": {"rendered": "<p><strong>1967:\u00a0</strong>The Castiles play at a rally dance at West Freehold School.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"21339\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1967-09-22-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1967-09-22.jpg?fit=1595%2C1645&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1595,1645\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1600167047&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1967-09-22\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1967-09-22.jpg?fit=758%2C782&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-21339 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1967-09-22.jpg?resize=758%2C782&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"782\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1967-09-22.jpg?w=1595&amp;ssl=1 1595w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1967-09-22.jpg?resize=291%2C300&amp;ssl=1 291w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1967-09-22.jpg?resize=993%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 993w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1967-09-22.jpg?resize=768%2C792&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1967-09-22.jpg?resize=1489%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 1489w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1973:\u00a0</strong>A scheduled gig in Miami opening for Richie Havens is cancelled to make room for mixing sessions for\u00a0<em>The Wild, The Innocent &amp; The E Street Shuffle\u00a0</em>at 914 Sound Studio in Blauvelt, New York.</p>\n<p><strong>1974:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band play an outdoor show at Kean College in Union, New Jersey, featuring the first known &#8220;A Love So Fine&#8221; (a work in progress that doesn&#8217;t even feature that lyric). Listen below&#8211;this also happens to be the earliest known recorded show with Max and Roy.</p>\n<div id=\"v-vTJrRGpc-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/vTJrRGpc?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/zE9ReiQpQkQ?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>1979:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band play their second of two famous &#8220;No Nukes&#8221; shows at Madison Square Garden under the aegis of Musicians United for Safe Energy (MUSE). Their performance of &#8220;Thunder Road&#8221; will become the official video for the song. Tom Petty, Jackson Browne, and Rosemary Butler join Bruce on-stage for the encore, but the show-closing &#8220;Quarter to Three&#8221; is marred by an uncharacteristically churlish Bruce embarrassing and removing his soon-to-be ex-girlfriend Lynn Goldsmith for taking photos without his permission. This show is available as part of Bruce\u2019s official archive series, and selections are available on video in the concert film,\u00a0<em>The Legendary 1979 No Nukes Concerts</em>.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/6P6q_zFHkj8?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent&#038;listType=playlist&#038;list=RD6P6q_zFHkj8\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/OtlvFQHfjEc?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/LzsAPhGpMkA?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/pzhqljeWqeo?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/NnRHijZRh34?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/N6W53QG69Fk?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/m2umNcwnjg8?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/1vBirXSN1J0?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/cyM3706b-h4?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>1984:\u00a0</strong>At his second Born in the U.S.A. show in Pittsburgh, Bruce begins a practice that stands to this day, donating money ($10,000) to a local steelworkers union and raising awareness by dedicating a song to them during the show.</p>\n<div id=\"v-ce15X4fu-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/ce15X4fu?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent&#038;listType=playlist&#038;list=PLJTyL9twk3zAKxlznwxlg-IRhr4tTPYKV\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p>Earlier in the day\u00a0<em>American Top 40</em> host Casey Kasem recaps the wedding of Steve and Maureen Van Zandt.</p>\n<audio class=\"wp-audio-shortcode\" id=\"audio-59695-1\" preload=\"none\" style=\"width: 100%;\" controls=\"controls\"><source type=\"audio/mpeg\" src=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/AT40-1985-09-22.mp3?_=1\" /><a href=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/AT40-1985-09-22.mp3\">https://estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/AT40-1985-09-22.mp3</a></audio>\n<p><strong>1985: </strong>A bad weather forecast prompts the postponement of a scheduled show at Denver&#8217;s Mile High Stadium. The evening ended up with clear skies, however, causing a bit of a backlash among fans and press.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"21340\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1985-09-22a/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1985-09-22a.jpg?fit=2437%2C1273&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"2437,1273\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1600167474&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1985-09-22a\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1985-09-22a.jpg?fit=758%2C396&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-21340 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1985-09-22a.jpg?resize=758%2C396&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"396\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1985-09-22a.jpg?w=2437&amp;ssl=1 2437w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1985-09-22a.jpg?resize=300%2C157&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1985-09-22a.jpg?resize=1024%2C535&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1985-09-22a.jpg?resize=768%2C401&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1985-09-22a.jpg?resize=1536%2C802&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1985-09-22a.jpg?resize=2048%2C1070&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1985-09-22a.jpg?w=2274&amp;ssl=1 2274w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"4494\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1985-0922/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1985-0922.jpg?fit=1229%2C613&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1229,613\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1985-0922\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1985-0922.jpg?fit=758%2C378&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-4494 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1985-0922.jpg?resize=758%2C378&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"378\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1985-0922.jpg?w=1229&amp;ssl=1 1229w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1985-0922.jpg?resize=300%2C150&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1985-0922.jpg?resize=768%2C383&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1985-0922.jpg?resize=1024%2C511&amp;ssl=1 1024w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1989:\u00a0</strong>Bruce joins Jimmy Cliff on stage at The Stone Pony in Asbury Park, where the two play &#8220;Trapped&#8221; in its original arrangement.</p>\n<div id=\"v-lr3uCktt-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/lr3uCktt?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><strong>1992:</strong> Bruce and his new touring band perform live for <em>MTV Unplugged\u00a0</em>at Warner Hollywood Studios, but after the opening &#8220;Red Headed Woman,&#8221; the band plugs in and rocks for the rest of the show. MTV rolls with it (&#8220;Hey, he&#8217;s Bruce Springsteen. He can do whatever he wants.&#8221;), and Bruce will release the show (in heavily edited and reassembled order) on CD and DVD as <em>In Concert/MTV Plugged</em>. However, the official releases omit several songs performed that night, including the last &#8220;Book of Dreams&#8221; for 13 years. See more of the missing performances below. Most of the show is available as streaming video from Bruce&#8217;s official YouTube account.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/djxSv0ZJpQ0?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/WoXRSsM_V-s?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/9HVJ8RiiUyM?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent&#038;listType=playlist&#038;list=RD9HVJ8RiiUyM\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/qfvu_H2Egf8?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"21349\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1992-09-22/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1992-09-22.jpg?fit=1254%2C1649&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1254,1649\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1600346857&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1992-09-22\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1992-09-22.jpg?fit=758%2C996&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-21349 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1992-09-22.jpg?resize=758%2C997&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"997\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1992-09-22.jpg?w=1254&amp;ssl=1 1254w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1992-09-22.jpg?resize=228%2C300&amp;ssl=1 228w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1992-09-22.jpg?resize=779%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 779w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1992-09-22.jpg?resize=768%2C1010&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1992-09-22.jpg?resize=1168%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 1168w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>2002:\u00a0</strong>The Rising Tour resumes at the Pepsi Center in Denver after a three-week break, and from this point forward the setlists will have more variety and spontaneity. This show features the tour premieres of &#8220;The Ties That Bind,&#8221; &#8220;Candy&#8217;s Room,&#8221; &#8220;Racing in the Street,&#8221; and a rare &#8220;I&#8217;m a Rocker.&#8221;</p>\n<div id=\"v-1RKhci5I-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/1RKhci5I?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/YuBp1GEL9uc?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>2003:\u00a0</strong><em>The River</em> is certified 5x multi-platinum by the Recording Industry Association of America.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent&#038;listType=playlist&#038;list=OLAK5uy_nQCRH689dsWcnQUgI1Tv3xx4UqJCzlHA4\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>2012:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band wrap up the summer leg of the Wrecking Ball Tour with a third show at MetLife Stadium in East Rutherford, where Bruce tour premieres &#8220;Cynthia,&#8221; &#8220;In the Midnight Hour,&#8221; &#8220;Into the Fire,&#8221; and &#8220;Meeting Across the River.&#8221; The show starts late due to inclement weather, and as a result, the band is still going strong when Bruce&#8217;s 63rd birthday arrives, and Bruce&#8217;s family comes on stage to present him with his cake. This show is available as part of Bruce&#8217;s official archive series.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/gY6SQab8oxM?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/pgdyb3dzfn4?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/TO73C-qhw8Q?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text