yle=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/OmCnCMdfsVw?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"21350\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/2012-09-22/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2012-09-22.jpg?fit=1441%2C1650&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1441,1650\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1600347242&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"2012-09-22\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2012-09-22.jpg?fit=758%2C868&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-21350 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2012-09-22.jpg?resize=758%2C868&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"868\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2012-09-22.jpg?w=1441&amp;ssl=1 1441w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2012-09-22.jpg?resize=262%2C300&amp;ssl=1 262w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2012-09-22.jpg?resize=894%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 894w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2012-09-22.jpg?resize=768%2C879&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2012-09-22.jpg?resize=1341%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 1341w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>2015:\u00a0</strong>Bruce makes a guest appearance with Jackson Browne and Teresa Williams on a show-closing &#8220;Take It Easy&#8221; and &#8220;Our Lady of the Well&#8221; at the Count Basie Theater in Red Bank.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/lurjHE-G8vI?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>2016:</strong> One week after wrapping the River Tour, Bruce is back on the circuit&#8211;this time on a publicity tour for his new autobiography,\u00a0<em>Born to Run</em>. Today, Bruce is interviewed by\u00a0<em>Skavlan</em>, a Norwegian-Swedish talk show. Later, he appears on\u00a0<em>The Late Show with Stephen Colbert</em>. Both appearances are broadcast the following day, Bruce&#8217;s 67th birthday.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/ewQyiONJGL4?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/zjYmcuN_9iU?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/7LvQNM_uLIs?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/SoOVIRpizL8?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/W8CsEqYCg68?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>2017:\u00a0</strong>Bruce holds a second private rehearsal for\u00a0<em>Springsteen on Broadway</em> at Monmouth University.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"21351\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/2017-09-22/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2017-09-22-scaled.jpg?fit=2560%2C1247&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"2560,1247\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1600347689&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"2017-09-22\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2017-09-22-scaled.jpg?fit=758%2C369&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-21351 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2017-09-22-scaled.jpg?resize=758%2C369&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"369\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2017-09-22-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;ssl=1 2560w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2017-09-22-scaled.jpg?resize=300%2C146&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2017-09-22-scaled.jpg?resize=1024%2C499&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2017-09-22-scaled.jpg?resize=768%2C374&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2017-09-22-scaled.jpg?resize=1536%2C748&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2017-09-22-scaled.jpg?resize=2048%2C998&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2017-09-22-scaled.jpg?w=2274&amp;ssl=1 2274w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n", "protected": false}, "excerpt": {"rendered": "<p>This date in Springsteen history is full of notable events: from the famous MTV &#8220;Plugged&#8221; show to the infamous &#8220;ex-girlfriend&#8217; show, from the very first &#8220;A Love So Fine&#8221; to the start of the talk show circuit for Bruce&#8217;s autobiography&#8211;all this and much more from this date.</p>\n", "protected": false}, "author": 1, "featured_media": 12844, "comment_status": "open", "ping_status": "open", "sticky": false, "template": "", "format": "standard", "meta": {"_monsterinsights_skip_tracking": false, "_monsterinsights_sitenote_active": false, "_monsterinsights_sitenote_note": "", "_monsterinsights_sitenote_category": 0, "_jetpack_newsletter_access": "", "_jetpack_dont_email_post_to_subs": false, "_jetpack_newsletter_tier_id": 0, "_jetpack_memberships_contains_paywalled_content": false, "_jetpack_memberships_contains_paid_content": false, "footnotes": "", "jetpack_publicize_message": "", "jetpack_publicize_feature_enabled": true, "jetpack_social_post_already_shared": true, "jetpack_social_options": {"image_generator_settings": {"template": "highway", "default_image_id": 0, "font": "", "enabled": false}, "version": 2}, "jetpack_post_was_ever_published": false}, "categories": [2], "tags": [784, 558, 303, 534, 567, 610, 484, 658, 1604, 1373, 1599, 957, 1601, 1602, 1360, 630, 1592, 68, 1018, 376, 1600, 1598, 774, 273, 11, 94, 1603, 59, 406, 985, 445], "class_list": ["post-59695", "post", "type-post", "status-publish", "format-standard", "has-post-thumbnail", "hentry", "category-kingdom-of-days", "tag-book-of-dreams", "tag-born-in-the-usa-tour", "tag-born-to-run", "tag-castiles", "tag-denver", "tag-east-rutherford", "tag-jackson-browne", "tag-jimmy-cliff", "tag-late-show-with-stephen-colbert", "tag-leap-of-faith", "tag-lynn-goldsmith", "tag-madison-square-garden", "tag-mtv-plugged", "tag-mtv-unplugged", "tag-muse", "tag-new-york-city", "tag-no-nukes", "tag-pittsburgh", "tag-quarter-to-three", "tag-rising-tour", "tag-rosalita-come-out-tonight", "tag-rosemary-butler", "tag-souls-of-the-departed", "tag-springsteen-on-broadway", "tag-stone-pony", "tag-take-it-easy", "tag-teresa-williams", "tag-thunder-road", "tag-tom-petty", "tag-world-tour-1992", "tag-wrecking-ball-tour"], "aioseo_notices": [], "jetpack_publicize_connections": [], "jetpack_featured_media_url": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/birthdayshow.jpg?fit=1600%2C1600&ssl=1", "jetpack_sharing_enabled": true, "jetpack_shortlink": "https://wp.me/p9w3Lk-fwP", "jetpack_likes_enabled": true, "jetpack-related-posts": [{"id": 57021, "url": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/06/06/kingdom-of-days-june-6-2/", "url_meta": {"origin": 59695, "position": 0}, "title": "June 6", "author": "Ken", "date": "June 6, 2025", "format": false, "excerpt": "Highlights from this date: a great recording of an early version of \"Rosalita,\" a guest-appearance by Joan Baez, an abandoned \"Dancing in the Dark\" video,, and more. Plus: the E Street Band (and the fans!) get an on-stage surprise in Indianapolis.", "rel": "", "context": "In &quot;Kingdom of Days&quot;", "block_context": {"text": "Kingdom of Days", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/category/kingdom-of-days/"}, "img": {"alt_text": "", "src": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/20060606_front.jpg?fit=626%2C605&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200", "width": 350, "height": 200, "srcset": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/20060606_front.jpg?fit=626%2C605&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200 1x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/20060606_front.jpg?fit=626%2C605&ssl=1&resize=525%2C300 1.5x"}, "classes": []}, {"id": 56001, "url": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/02/26/kingdom-of-days-february-26-2/", "url_meta": {"origin": 59695, "position": 1}, "title": "February 26", "author": "Ken", "date": "February 26, 2025", "format": false, "excerpt": "An insanely eventful day in Bruce history with gigs galore, Grammy Awards, and TV appearances. Check out the highlights, including an amazing cover of \"Stayin' Alive\" and a barely-pre-reunion clip from Conan O'Brian.", "rel": "", "context": "In &quot;Kingdom of Days&quot;", "block_context": {"text": "Kingdom of Days", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/category/kingdom-of-days/"}, "img": {"alt_text": "", "src": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/officiallivedownloads_2014-02-26.jpg?fit=800%2C800&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200", "width": 350, "height": 200, "srcset": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/officiallivedownloads_2014-02-26.jpg?fit=800%2C800&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200 1x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/officiallivedownloads_2014-02-26.jpg?fit=800%2C800&ssl=1&resize=525%2C300 1.5x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/officiallivedownloads_2014-02-26.jpg?fit=800%2C800&ssl=1&resize=700%2C400 2x"}, "classes": []}, {"id": 59657, "url": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/09/16/kingdom-of-days-september-16-2/", "url_meta": {"origin": 59695, "position": 2}, "title": "September 16", "author": "Ken", "date": "September 16, 2025", "format": false, "excerpt": "On this date: A performance by the Castiles that would be officially released almost 50 years later, Bruce uploads a new, under-the-radar cover, and the one and only performance to date of \"Let's Be Friends (Skin to Skin).\" Lots more highlights inside.", "rel": "", "context": "In &quot;Kingdom of Days&quot;", "block_context": {"text": "Kingdom of Days", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/category/kingdom-of-days/"}, "img": {"alt_text": "", "src": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/19780916_2_front-1.jpg?fit=930%2C799&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200", "width": 350, "height": 200, "srcset": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/19780916_2_front-1.jpg?fit=930%2C799&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200 1x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/19780916_2_front-1.jpg?fit=930%2C799&ssl=1&resize=525%2C300 1.5x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/19780916_2_front-1.jpg?fit=930%2C799&ssl=1&resize=700%2C400 2x"}, "classes": []}, {"id": 57023, "url": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/06/08/kingdom-of-days-june-8-2/", "url_meta": {"origin": 59695, "position": 3}, "title": "June 8", "author": "Ken", "date": "June 8, 2025", "format": false, "excerpt": "Happy wedding anniversary, Bruce and Patti! Also on this date: Bruce plays a Born in the U.S.A. warm-up gig at The Stone Pony--listen to the first public airing of much of the album. Plus: the stadium breaker!", "rel": "", "context": "In &quot;Kingdom of Days&quot;", "block_context": {"text": "Kingdom of Days", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/category/kingdom-of-days/"}, "img": {"alt_text": "", "src": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/brucepatti.jpg?fit=640%2C640&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200", "width": 350, "height": 200, "srcset": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/brucepatti.jpg?fit=640%2C640&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200 1x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/brucepatti.jpg?fit=640%2C640&ssl=1&resize=525%2C300 1.5x"}, "classes": []}, {"id": 59681, "url": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/09/17/kingdom-of-days-september-17-2/", "url_meta": {"origin": 59695, "position": 4}, "title": "September 17", "author": "Ken", "date": "September 17, 2025", "format": false, "excerpt": "On this date: Born to Run hits #1, Bruce debuts his duet with Sting on \"Every Breath You Take,\" and a tantalizing audio glimpse of a still-unreleased, never-performed original song.", "rel": "", "context": "In &quot;Kingdom of Days&quot;", "block_context": {"text": "Kingdom of Days", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/category/kingdom-of-days/"}, "img": {"alt_text": "", "src": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/19780917_5_front.jpg?fit=1200%2C987&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200", "width": 350, "height": 200, "srcset": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/19780917_5_front.jpg?fit=1200%2C987&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200 1x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/19780917_5_front.jpg?fit=1200%2C987&ssl=1&resize=525%2C300 1.5x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/19780917_5_front.jpg?fit=1200%2C987&ssl=1&resize=700%2C400 2x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/19780917_5_front.jpg?fit=1200%2C987&ssl=1&resize=1050%2C600 3x"}, "classes": []}, {"id": 57559, "url": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/07/02/kingdom-of-days-july-2-2/", "url_meta": {"origin": 59695, "position": 5}, "title": "July 2", "author": "Ken", "date": "July 2, 2025", "format": false, "excerpt": "Happy birthday \"Professor\" Roy Bittan! Also on this date: Bruce films his first movie role, opens the Meadowlands, and plays \"Jersey Girl\" for the first time. Plus: CBS profiles Clarence, and Mike Appel takes legal action to stop Bruce from recording.", "rel": "", "context": "In &quot;Kingdom of Days&qu